<br></br>
<h2>Calculate span of control to scale your organization</h2>
<p>It doesn‚Äôt matter whether your company has 10 or 1,000 people. Companies of all sizes can benefit from rethinking the ideal span of control for each managerial role‚Äîespecially in <a href="https://tomtunguz.com/secret-of-scaling-teams/" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank">stages of intense growth</a> or restructuring. </p>
<p>Use this guide to thoughtfully pair managers with direct reports. Keep teams small enough to be manageable for leaders but large enough to give employees some autonomy over their work. With this intentional approach to team structuring, your company will have a solid foundation for scaling.</p></div>";s:10:"post_title";s:58:"What‚Äôs a manageable span of control? (+ free calculator)";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:157:"Understand the importance of span of control, the pros and cons of wide and narrow spans and use a new framework to calculate a role's ideal span of control.";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:70:"httpswww-charthop-comblogbest-practicesspan-of-control-free-calculator";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2022-05-02 10:45:26";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2022-05-02 10:45:26";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:130:"https://charthop.1devserver.co.uk/resources/%content_type%/%resource_category%/whats-a-manageable-span-of-control-free-calculator/";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:9:"resources";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}}